<br>
The video you saw, which if I'm guessing correctly is the same one I have, is an old video of the pre-revamp ST. It's also the old ST that was pre-awakening, so you see the old warders in them (damn nice video btw <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ). <br>
<br>
The named golems are easy to handle if you get them solo so that shouldn't be a problem for you guys (if you can take out the st key holders in the first place, you can take out the named golems).  The ancient dragons at the bottom may be some trouble for you, but by no means too difficult. You'll definitely need a large raiding party for the dragons though.<br>
<br>
Other than that, send your monks in to learn the place and pull stuff for you and you should be fine. Always have tanks ready to tank mez, and try not to let stuff gate (thats always a given for like...every raid <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ).<br>
